        <T> T get(Class<T> expectedType,
          String name)
        Access a record field value. IMPORTANT: it is always better to use the typed accessors and the optional flavor when the entry is nullable.
        Type Parameters:
        T - the type of expectedType.
        Parameters:
        expectedType - the expected type for the column.
        name - the name of the column.
        Returns:
        the column value.
